{"id": 1283, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x嘉实多磁护】生活中有哪些保护，少了你才会发现不习惯？", "description": "手机在没带充电宝的那天没电，棉条买小了…一种“离开了才觉得刻骨铭心”式关怀。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5693, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201610202105454BrlECHWuef0x1vK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-21T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 126464, "content": "Adblock", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 126467, "content": "上课时，在我以为无论如何都不会叫我的时候，突然听到了我的名字（一脸懵逼）", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804942}, {"id": 126469, "content": "姨妈第一天却只剩下一只小容量棉条。整个人都方了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746370}, {"id": 126470, "content": "新衣服衣领里侧标签略扎。。。保持军姿脖子才能愉快", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801633}, {"id": 126473, "content": "走到半路下起雨来，而且没带伞。。。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804899}, {"id": 126218, "content": "临近姨妈来的那几天出门 发现没有带姨妈巾", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508751}, {"id": 126474, "content": "没戴眼镜没带水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803826}, {"id": 126730, "content": "坐火车忘带kindle", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806175}, {"id": 128267, "content": "出门带手机忘记带充电宝，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704221}, {"id": 126220, "content": "去乐视为了补刀剑，才发现没有广告的b站有多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743270}, {"id": 126476, "content": "出门没带手机…带了手机发现没带充电器（快充手机电池容量好小）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790098}, {"id": 126221, "content": "上课没带耳机=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666428}, {"id": 126222, "content": "去乐视补了个番，才发现没有广告的b站有多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743270}, {"id": 126478, "content": "被快递放鸽子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277949}, {"id": 126479, "content": "脑子要带", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790227}, {"id": 126224, "content": "出门没带手机 瞬间懵逼，出门都不知道干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 274, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803675}, {"id": 126225, "content": "奥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626549}, {"id": 126481, "content": "哈哈哈，嘉实多磁护，未启动 先保护 时刻保护", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805059}, {"id": 126482, "content": "开车没有嘉实多磁护机油，我也觉得不习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805059}, {"id": 126227, "content": "刚把门关上一摸口袋发现钥匙在门那头，而我在门这头", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636730}, {"id": 130580, "content": "没带纸巾口香糖，可以听音乐的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799350}, {"id": 126485, "content": "嘉实多磁护，未启动，先保护", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805081}, {"id": 126486, "content": "钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773277}, {"id": 126487, "content": "耳机，想听歌的时候才发现耳机不在", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561996}, {"id": 126232, "content": "来例假的前几天，晚上担心胡思乱想", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803658}, {"id": 126488, "content": "胸罩小了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805090}, {"id": 126233, "content": "耳机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 126234, "content": "睡觉时候的抱枕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 126490, "content": "拉屎发现厕所没纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798365}, {"id": 126235, "content": "流量，WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 126491, "content": "没穿好看的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160518}, {"id": 126236, "content": "我妈的唠叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803658}, {"id": 126493, "content": "嘉实多磁护：未启动，先保护，时刻保护", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805114}, {"id": 126238, "content": "工作的时候天天厌班，裸辞了发现有个公司为自己遮风避雨多么好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197691}, {"id": 126494, "content": "保持不期待的平常心", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805122}, {"id": 126240, "content": "出门没带钱包 忘带手机 一整天精神恍惚", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203199}, {"id": 126496, "content": "这是一篇连载的故事（1）一直觉得 时刻保护我的 一定是我们家的冰箱 台风天 打开冰箱的一瞬 眼泪掉下来 \n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698826}, {"id": 126752, "content": "没穿胸罩出门感觉外套都随时会掉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 126241, "content": "出门带伞带纸巾带充电宝带钥匙", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 126497, "content": "这是一篇连载的故事（2）转身拿出手机 想点一碗热气腾腾的麻辣烫抚慰一下我受伤的心灵 这个时候手机应该是我最大的依靠了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698826}, {"id": 126498, "content": "没带手机绝对无法习惯！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804760}, {"id": 126243, "content": "这个月例假迟了10，每一天都不好过", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 126499, "content": "（3）转念想 外卖小哥不容易 万一骑车陷水坑里 这可是大罪过 好蓝瘦 得 外卖也靠不住 时刻保护我的 还是只有我自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698826}, {"id": 126244, "content": "必然是忘带的纸巾阿", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632917}, {"id": 126500, "content": "（4）出门取车 哼着小调去吃我心心念念的麻辣烫 四周寂静无声 哎 我这车怎么这么好 发动机一点儿噪音也没有 还是我的车靠谱 时刻保护我不挨饿 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698826}, {"id": 128548, "content": "没带充电宝 没有餐巾纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 126246, "content": "老师按顺序提问，结果突然变方式，我还在走神", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725147}, {"id": 126247, "content": "老师按顺序提问，结果突然变方式，我还在走神", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725147}, {"id": 126503, "content": "（5）这说明一个什么问题 要想我不挨饿 时刻被保护着 就得我的车被保护着 那么他用什么机油呢 这是个好问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698826}, {"id": 126248, "content": "上班没带手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66632}]}